## 6. Preventive Measures
To prevent a recurrence of this incident, the following steps will be implemented:
* [cite_start]**Log Management:** Configure `logrotate` for all application and system log paths. [cite: 41]
* [cite_start]**Tiered Monitoring:** Set a **Warning** alert at 75% and a **Critical** alert at 85% to allow for proactive intervention. [cite: 42]
* [cite_start]**Automated Cleanup:** Implement `systemd-tmpfiles` to manage `/tmp` data automatically. [cite: 43]
* [cite_start]**Automation:** Deploy a cron job to automatically audit and clean old backup/dump files. [cite: 44]

